report and list crud
    a calculation should not exist outside of a test, a test should not exist outside of a report, so fill out basic crud for test and reports and then update the e2e test
    valid parent entity constraint - create a domain service interface in child domain to ensure parent entity is valid, concrete interface in domain service dir
    create test helpers to help seed data, maybe through the test server for proper e2e, maybe direct in the repositories, maybe both

calculation linking
    figure out ability to have test calculation B reference an output of test calculation A as an input
    determine if the calculation owns this or the test does

lab test run
    lab report needs ability to have global inputs that can be consumed by calculations
        idea: labtestinput domain that has its own repository and parent test id similar to calculation
        ^handle any additional needs via domain service, similar to calculation->test actions
    ability to build dependency graphs between calculations, verify if all tests can be run, and then execute them all

test run / calculation execution ideas
    test domain service
        verify all test inputs are filled in before trying to eval?
    calculation domain or service
        domain calculation has the function to execute the calculation and receives parameters
        calculation being solvable might need to be a domain service, though receiving a list of parameters might work for just domain
    infra/store should have the specialized queries
        calculation repository
            FindInitialSolveableByTestID - paginated query to find calculations that have no inputs or test inputs/constants
            FindUnsolvedByTestID - paginated query for no cached result
        calculation link repository
            FindLinksBySourceOutputs - paginated query to find links for source and target, a domain service should then filter those by solved
    lab test will own domain service that orchestrates solving a full test
        validate that all test inputs are filled
        phase 1: initially solveable calculations
            iterator of calculations that have no inputs or have test inputs/const
        phase 2: cascade crawl
            iterator of calculations that have all dependent calculations solved
            need some mechanism in this phase to avoid loops
            all calculations have a set result = done

